import { AppBar, Box, Button, Container, Toolbar, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

export default function Navbar() {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <AppBar className="navbar" position="static" color="transparent" elevation={0}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Toolbar sx={{ justifyContent: "space-between", paddingY: "1rem" }}>
          <Typography variant="h6">
            <Link to="/" style={{ textDecoration: "none", color: "#fff" }}>
              Bio-Inka
            </Link>
          </Typography>
          <Box>
            <Button variant="text" color="inherit" onClick={() => navigate("/inicio/geo")} sx={{ marginX: '0.5rem' }}>
              Georreferenciaci√≥n
            </Button>
            <Button variant="text" color="inherit" onClick={() => navigate("/inicio/iniciova")} sx={{ marginX: '0.5rem' }}>
              Destacados
            </Button>
            <Button variant="text" color="inherit" onClick={() => navigate("/inicio/about")} sx={{ marginX: '0.5rem' }}>
              Acerca de nosotros
            </Button>
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" onClick={() => navigate("/inicio/login")} sx={{ marginX: '0.5rem' }}>
              Log-In
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>
    </AppBar>
  );
}
